This is a list of things to add or improve in the suite berry.
No special order.

1. Add suport for noncolinear calculations
2. Implement more verification of initial conditions in each run
3. Add calculations of properties derived from Berry curvature
4. Add calculation of other nonlinear optical properties from Berry connection
